title: Unreal Tournemant 3 Soundtrack
description:
I extracted the soundtrack to Ogg Vorbis File, which can be played on Winamp player or any Andriod phones. There are many small files because music changes ingame (eg when you pick up a flag), so dont be confused ;-).


You can also extract the files yourselves by downloading the Oggextractor on http://moriya.ca/oggextract/ and open the files with oggextract.exe.

The music files could be located in the folder C:Users(User's PC)GamesUnreal Tournament 3UTGameCookedPCSounds or C:Programmes x86(R.G Mechanics or Steam or...)Unreal Tournament 3UTGameCookedPCSounds.

The extractor should fould in C:Users(User's PC)Downloads.
